Core/

EngineGame.cs — Base game loop (Start, Update, FixedUpdate). Entry point of the engine/game.

Time.cs — Tracks deltaTime, fixedDeltaTime, total runtime, and frame count.

IUpdatable.cs / IFixedUpdatable.cs — Interfaces for objects that update every frame or each physics step.

IService.cs / ServiceLocator.cs — Implements service locator pattern for global engine systems (Input, Audio, Physics, etc.).

Scenes/

Scene.cs — Contains all game objects/entities for a single scene.

SceneManager.cs — Manages switching between scenes and active scene tracking.

SceneLoader.cs — Handles asynchronous scene loading/unloading and resource preparation.

Scenes/Graphics/

Renderer2D.cs — Centralized sprite batcher and renderer for 2D graphics and UI.

Sprite.cs — Encapsulates drawable sprite data: texture, transform, color.

Texture.cs — Wrapper around MonoGame Texture2D with additional metadata.

Material.cs — Defines rendering properties (blend mode, shader, opacity).

Camera2D.cs — 2D camera supporting position, zoom, rotation, and viewport.

Input/

InputSystem.cs — Central manager updating all registered input devices.

IInputDevice.cs — Base interface for any input device.

KeyboardDevice.cs — Implements keyboard input (key down, key up, key held).

MouseDevice.cs — Implements mouse input (buttons, position, scroll).
(Extensible: can add GamepadDevice, TouchDevice, NetworkInput, etc.)

Physics/

Rigidbody2D.cs — Represents a physics body (mass, velocity, forces, integration).

Collider2D.cs — Abstract base for all colliders (AABB, Circle, etc.).

AABB.cs — Axis-Aligned Bounding Box collider implementation.

PhysicsWorld.cs — Runs physics simulation and resolves collisions each fixed step.

Collision.cs — Stores collision info and contact resolution data.

Audio/

AudioSystem.cs — Global sound manager that initializes the audio engine.

AudioSource.cs — Plays sound clips, supporting volume, mute, loop, and priority.

UI/

UIElement.cs — Base class for all UI components (position, size, visibility).

UILabel.cs — Displays static or dynamic text.

UIButton.cs — Clickable button with callback events.

UISlider.cs — Slider with min/max value and user interaction.

UIDropdown.cs — Dropdown list selection menu.

UIInputField.cs — Editable text input field.

UILayout.cs — Automatic positioning/layout of UI elements (horizontal, vertical, grid).

Assets/

AssetManifest.cs — Metadata about assets (paths, types, dependencies).

AssetManager.cs — Loads/unloads assets (textures, sounds, prefabs) and manages references.

Packaging/

PackageExporter.cs — Bundles project content into .renpkg packages (similar to Unity packages).

PackageImporter.cs — Imports external packages into the engine.

PackageManifest.cs — Stores metadata for each package (name, version, dependencies).

Meta

Directory.Structure — Official folder tree for engine source files.

Brief.Info — Documentation describing the purpose of each file/folder in the engine.